alwaysApply: true
---

name: concise-answers
description: Ensure all assistant responses are minimal and concise.
rules:
  - When responding to user questions or comments, keep the response as brief and to-the-point as possible.
  - Avoid unnecessary elaboration, repetition, or filler.
  - Use simple, direct language.
  - Only expand when the user explicitly asks for more detail or clarification.
